item.title: Only can see my custom items when female
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

Items have typically 3 models. Male wield, female wield, and then drop model. Drop models are for your inventory/equip icons (And any icon on interface you see). The other two are rather self explanatory.

Most weapons and custom items (made by not Jagex) don’t have more than the single wield model and the drop model. If that’s the case, the male and female wields are the same.
